  "tells": [
    "Use Brainstorm to dig deep, then follow up with Ponder to shuffle unfavorable cards on top.",
    "Cast Lorien Revealed to search for Volatile Fjord, ensuring consistent red mana access.",
    "Time Cast into the Fire to clear multiple tokens or lands simultaneously for maximum efficiency.",
    "Retain Monarch by avoiding combat damage to draw an extra card each turn.",
    "Common mistakes include overcommitting to Lorien Revealed without follow-up, holding up too many counterspells and missing early interaction windows, and underestimating Skred\u2019s vulnerability to board wipes."
